# Blog List App (React.js)

A responsive blog listing application built using *React.js*. It displays blog cards with dynamic rendering and a clean UI.

## 🚀 Features

- Dynamic blog list rendering using props
- Responsive design using CSS
- Component-based structure
- Clean layout and hover effects

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- React.js
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

## 📁 How to Run Locally

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Sejal0w/BlogList.js
cd BlogList.js
npm install
npm start
